{
  "id": "adv_main_03_13_01",
  "title": "BIG4編1章61話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――どりきゅんとの対決　一週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One week before the showdown with DoriKyun",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.8399999618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "これで今日のメニューはおしまいです\n皆さん、練習お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's all for today's menu‚\nEveryone‚ good work today‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様ー。もう芽衣、へとへとだよ\nでも今日の練習もすっごい充実してたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ Mei's exhausted‚\nBut today's practice was super fulfilling!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスとの合同練習以来、実力アップは当然だけど\n集中力もぐんと上がってる実感があるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since our joint practice with IIIX‚ our skills have improved‚ of course‚\nbut I also feel like our concentration has increased dramatically‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。mihoさん達には本当に感謝しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ We have to thank miho-san and the others‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0260315735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、みなさん。ちょっといいかしら\n提案がありますの。聞いて下さる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‚‚‚Um‚ everyone‚ May I have a moment of your time?\nI have a proposal‚ Will you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "すず？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu? What's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3955100695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今度のどりきゅんとの決戦――\n私は、琴乃にセンターを譲りますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For our upcoming showdown with DoriKyun――\nI will relinquish my position as center to Kotono‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5853285312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 49.252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "え、すずちゃん！？　どうして？　今度のバトルの\nセンターはすずちゃんでいくって決めてたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What‚ Suzu-chan!? Why? We decided\nthat you would be center for the next battle‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。練習だって、ずっとそのつもりで\nしてたじゃない。対決まであと少しなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ We've been practicing with that in mind‚\nThe showdown is just around the corner‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "時間がないから、そう言っているんです\nみなさんも気付いているはずですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's exactly why I'm saying this‚ because we don't have time‚\nI believe you all have noticed as well‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3601763883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "合同練習の後からずっと考えていました。悔しいですが\n私が真のセンターになるには、まだ時間が必要です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been thinking about it ever since our joint practice‚ It's frustrating‚ but‚‚‚\nI still need more time to become a true center‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6268430549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "先日のスリクスとのライブバトルでは、私のセンターと\n琴乃のセンター、両方を試したでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In our recent live battle with IIIX‚ we tried\nboth me and Kotono as center‚ didn't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0239576577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がセンターの時の方がスコアが高かった\n……それに、みんな手応えを感じていたはずですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The score was higher when Kotono was center‚\n‚‚‚And I believe you all felt it‚ too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1935102302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 107.7333320618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……そうかもしれませんけど\n……すずちゃんはそれでいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That‚‚‚ may be true‚ but‚‚‚\n‚‚‚Are you sure about this‚ Suzu-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "冷静に考えた結果ですわ。決戦までの数少ない時間を\n両方のパターンに使う暇なんてありませんわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the result of careful consideration‚ We don't have the luxury\nof wasting the little time we have until the showdown on trying both patterns‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.686344544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3530113219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "勝ち負けだけが全てじゃない。それは分かっていますわ\nでも、勝てる確率が高い方法があるのにそれを選ばない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ why do you all look so glum?\nI'm not the type to be discouraged by something like this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5444606223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのは、ここまで頑張ってきた自分達に対しても\n……そしてどりきゅんに対しても、失礼というものです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're not going to disappear just because we beat DoriKyun!\nAnd besides‚ if Kotono gets even a little complacent‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4811497289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "この戦いにかける琴乃の想いも、よく分かっていますわ\nだから……あなたを信じて、センターの座を託します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand Kotono's feelings about this battle very well‚\nSo‚‚‚ I trust you‚ I entrust the position of center to you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4811497289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "すず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚‚‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8144801217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、みんなして何を浮かない顔をしていますの？\nこの程度のこと、気にする私ではありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ why the long faces?\nI'm not the type to worry about something like this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.328911185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 163.866653188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんに勝って\nそれで私達の道が終わる訳ではないのですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll beat DoriKyun‚\nand that won't be the end of our journey!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2407918622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃が少しでも慢心したら\nすぐにセンターの座を奪い取りますわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And besides‚ if Kotono gets even a little complacent‚‚‚\nI'll snatch the center position back in a heartbeat‚ you hear?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.8622445183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。どりきゅんとのバトルでは\n私がセンターを預かる。今度こそ絶対に、勝とう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‚‚‚Alright‚ I'll take the center position for the battle with DoriKyun‚\nThis time‚ we'll win for sure‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.2333216349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "さて、私はちょっと気分転換をしてきますわ\nすぐに戻って来ますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm going to go clear my head for a bit‚\nI'll be back soon‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.9422413902,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.333222000005,
          "startTime": 191.7422413902
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……うん。行ってらっしゃい、すず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚‚‚ yeah‚ See you later‚ Suzu‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.4089081682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4795201854
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.4795201854
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 200.7295201854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
